aim_mac10foshizzle
by: naklajat

I took a break from mapping and made this :) You get a new Mac10 at the beginning of each new round, no need to throw it down.

=====================

It has cubemaps and an overview(:D), and I made it so the map gives you full ammo and takes away your pistol. Supports 32 players, and while that would be nuts, I recommend 12-20. The bots work decent too, though they don't quite grasp the aim_ concept...
